Admissions & Enrollment

Begin your child's journey to excellence. We welcome students who are eager to learn and grow.

Admission Requirements
Please prepare the following documents for your application.

For New Students:

  • • Completed application form
  • • Birth certificate (original and photocopy)
  • • Report card from previous school
  • • Certificate of good moral character
  • • Medical certificate
  • • 2x2 ID photos (4 pieces)
  • • Entrance examination (scheduled after application)

For Transferees:

  • • All requirements for new students
  • • Transfer credentials (Form 137)
  • • Certificate of enrollment from previous school
  • • Honorable dismissal

Important Dates:

• Application Period: March - May

• Entrance Exam: April - May

• Enrollment: June
